Class Summary
Command  
ReadConfiguration Created when a CMD_CONF message has been read in the Bluetooth socket's input stream
ReadEnd Created when a CMD_END message has been read in the Bluetooth socket's input stream
ReadEndHash Created when an CMD_ENDHASH message has been read in the Bluetooth socket's input stream
ReadHash Created when an CMD_HASH message has been read in the Bluetooth socket's input stream.

WriteConfiguration The first command that an async connection has to enqueue; writes the local configuration to the Bluetooth socket's output stream
WriteEnd Enqueue this command when all the updates has been sent to the remote device.
WriteEndHash Created when the local device finished to write his TweetHashes on the Bluetooth socket's output stream.
WriteHash Created to write a single TweetHash on a Bluetooth socket.
WriteTweet Created to write a single Tweet on a Bluetooth socket.
